{"tid":1759800,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以係職工盟開工會?","createTime":"2019-11-28T00:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T03:17:39.000Z","uid":262072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0d03f8bf671a06562017627cdb5b9a1a862aa5","tid":1759800,"uid":262072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:24:34.000Z","msg":"如題，佢個網冇寫到"},{"pid":"03c42038b2b9d3828156dffcceedfd5dd496c977","tid":1759800,"uid":262072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:29:39.000Z","msg":"我間公司有一個人返工，我想開間工會。"},{"pid":"0e4c4c8b245327a363684d26f09f8e9c100eae61","tid":1759800,"uid":292362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:01:06.000Z","msg":"仲用職工盟? <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cc414ac1e9364e9a80fbeb15dc522f7c24d56e","tid":1759800,"uid":333752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d0d03f8bf671a06562017627cdb5b9a1a862aa5","tid":1759800,"uid":262072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:24:34.000Z","msg":"如題，佢個網冇寫到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"叫埋身邊7個同事/朋友就可以成立1個工會,成為勞工界登記選民(呢個界別選民=工會)。<br />\n如有5000人做左, 都已經多5000/7=700幾個登記選民, 可以直接將手足送入勞工界功能組別於立法會(輕鬆3席全取)&amp;特首選委(60席)<br />\n<br />\n嗰D會話「要真普選啊，爭咩功能組別啊？」其實任何有得做嘅野都要做。何況呢個係無咩cost而可以有效地作出影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/變天最關鍵的特首選委界別-唔夠四個月就靜靜輸了\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AE%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E5%A7%94%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5-%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E5%9B%9B%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%B1%E9%9D%9C%E9%9D%9C%E8%BC%B8%E4%BA%86&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=f656f007\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AE%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%80%E9%97%9C%E9%8D%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E9%81%B8%E5%A7%94%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5-%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E5%9B%9B%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%B0%B1%E9%9D%9C%E9%9D%9C%E8%BC%B8%E4%BA%86&h=453e99c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/變天最關鍵的特首選委界別-唔夠四個月就靜靜輸了</a><br />\n<br />\n表格(只填第1&amp;第2份&amp;第4&amp;5就得）：<a href=\"https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2FunionsforHK&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=7ba80ac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK</a><br />\n填完連埋7個人工作證明（如卡片）Scan去： rtu@labour.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n注意：名唔可以重複現有工會，所以最好起個獨特d嘅名<br />\n可入去search下有冇撞名。（最新統計名單得2017年）&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/rtu/ASR2017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Frtu%2FASR2017.pdf&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=4b44372c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/rtu/ASR2017.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n（辦事處地址，是但填個屋企地址都得）<br />\n<br />\nsend埋約30日就正式成立!"}]}